Review:Header: Stylish way to sport a backpack
Review_Text: After moving out of the diaper bag phase, I was looking for something cute, but functional to use for theme parks and outings. This backpack is very cute, has lots of pockets and plenty of room for snacks, jackets, diapers and wipes, among other things. It cost a bit more than I would have liked to spend, but in the end I am happy to have something feminine, as well as useful.

Product_Name: Lewis N. Clark Comfort Neck Pillow
Review:Header: I trust Kohl's and what they have to offer.
Review_Text: I at times get a stiff neck. It makes it very hard to sleep with this pain in my neck. My wife went online at Kohl's and bought me a dark red pillow the U shape kind and I have to tell you that darn pillow works. It place it under my neck and it supported my neck very well enough for me to sleep. I would say if you have pain in your neck buy one from online Kohl's if don't work you can always send it back. I have the pillow for a month and I do sleep better.

Product_Name: Lewis N. Clark Comfort Neck Pillow

Review_Text: I've had numerous neck surgeries and this neck pillow is perfect for that support I need when my neck hurts. I even sleep with it to give me that extra support and a precaution that I don't let my neck droop while sleeping.

Product_Name: Lewis N. Clark Comfort Neck Pillow
Review_Text: I bought this product for an elderly lady b/c she falls asleep in her chair and her head bobs. This helps control her neck from moving when she sleeps thus decreasing her neck pain. It works well

Product_Name: Lewis N. Clark Comfort Neck Pillow
Review_Text: I've owned many neck pillows and this one is my favorite! The fleecy fabric covers the entire pillow so there is no cold side. The filling seems to be a thick, supportive foam instead of beads so you don't just "sink in". It retains its shape and is substantial enough to replace a conventional pillow. I liked it so much I bought a second for keeping at the cabin!

Product_Name: Lewis N. Clark Comfort Neck Pillow
Review_Text: We just got back from a trip to China and these saved us on the 13 hour plane ride. They are just as described, soft almost fleece material. Would definitely recommend if that's what you're looking for!
